@startuml
title Sequence Diagram: User Views Research Details

actor User
participant "Frontend/UI (React)" as UI
participant "Backend/API" as API
participant "Auth Middleware (JWT)" as AUTH
database "Database (Neon)" as DB

User -> UI: Navigate to /case/{id}

UI -> API: GET /trl/case/{id} (JWT)
API -> AUTH: Verify token
AUTH --> API: Token valid
API -> DB: Fetch case by id
DB --> API: Case data
API --> UI: Return case data

par Fetch related data
    UI -> API: GET /trl/appointment/{id}
    API -> DB: Fetch appointments
    DB --> API: Appointment data
    API --> UI: Return appointments

    UI -> API: GET /trl/coordinator/{id}
    API -> DB: Fetch coordinator
    DB --> API: Coordinator data
    API --> UI: Return coordinator

    UI -> API: GET /trl/ip/{id}
    API -> DB: Fetch IP data
    DB --> API: IP records
    API --> UI: Return IP data

    UI -> API: GET /trl/supportment/{id}
    API -> DB: Fetch support data
    DB --> API: Support data
    API --> UI: Return support data

    UI -> API: GET /trl/assessment/{id}
    API -> DB: Fetch assessment
    DB --> API: Assessment data
    API --> UI: Return assessment
end

UI -> API: GET /researcher/{researcher_id}
API -> DB: Fetch researcher info
DB --> API: Researcher data
API --> UI: Return researcher data

UI --> User: Display full research details page

@enduml